title: Proxeeus - Ayahuasca (Ohm Mind Remix)
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Unreleased version of Ohm Mind's remix for 'Ayahuasca' track by Proxeeus, available as bonus digital download for limited digipak edition of 'Birds Will Go To Heaven' album. Pre-order/download here: http://bit.ly/get-birds
